Package: chatAI4R
Type: Package
Title: Chat-based Interactive Artificial Intelligence for R
Version: 0.0.4
Date: 2023-07-20
Authors@R: c(person("Satoshi", "Kume", 
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "satoshi.kume.1984@gmail.com"))
Description: chatAI4R provides a seamless interface for integrating the 
    OpenAI API (see <https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference>) and 
    other APIs into R. This package leverages large language model (LLM)-based 
    AI techniques, enabling efficient knowledge discovery and data analysis.
    In addition, this package includes functionality for performing 
    image generation such as txt2img and img2img using the DALLÂ·E 2 and 
    Stable Diffusion APIs.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
